Who came back because
Irene threatened to put
the dog to sleep if he didn't.

53
00:05:41,717 --> 00:05:46,554
Your brother Dennis
is professor
at Johns Hopkins.

54
00:05:46,722 --> 00:05:49,181
He's married to, uh, Betsy.

55
