Your Uncle Milton lost all of his money.

59
00:06:11,663 --> 00:06:13,622
And some other people's.

60
00:06:13,790 --> 00:06:18,210
In a pyramid scheme.
Don't mention the IRS
or the federal prisons system.

61
00:06:18,378 --> 00:06:20,880
Your mother's Barbara, your father's Cliff

62
00:06:22,090 --> 00:06:25,968
My father has electric trains.
Really?

63
00:06:26,136 --> 00:06:29,055
Am I what they had in mind?

64
00:06:29,222 --> 00:06:33,476
Oh, Walter, they're gonna love you!

65
00:06:34,478 --> 00:06:35,811
