I'm 8.

207
00:13:54,876 --> 00:13:56,710
FIELDSTONE:
Eight? How come you're up so late?

208
00:13:56,878 --> 00:13:58,295
JONAH:
It's not that late in Seattle.

209
00:13:58,463 --> 00:14:00,130
FIELDSTONE:
Oh, of course,
you're absolutely right.

210
00:14:00,298 --> 00:14:02,591
