00:45:07,413 --> 00:45:11,416
Time, distance,
nothing could separate them
because they knew.

692
00:45:11,584 --> 00:45:15,754
It was right. It was real. It was...
It's a movie.

693
00:45:15,922 --> 00:45:17,714
That's your problem.
You don't wanna be in love.

