of letters to strangers.

698
00:45:31,312 --> 00:45:34,689
I know that.
You think I don't
know that?

699
00:45:34,857 --> 00:45:38,443
What about Walter?
Oh, Walter.

700
00:45:38,611 --> 00:45:41,446
