what he's like by just looking
at him, but you can't.

703
00:45:48,830 --> 00:45:51,415
I should write something in this about magic.

704
00:45:51,582 --> 00:45:53,917
What?
Something! What if I never meet him?

705
00:45:54,085 --> 00:45:56,753
