00:46:03,511 --> 00:46:05,387
On the top of the Empire State Building.

710
00:46:06,889 --> 00:46:09,766
Sunset, Valentine's Day.

711
00:46:10,852 --> 00:46:14,062
I'll be in New
York with Walter.
I can squeeze it in.

712
00:46:15,148 --> 00:46:18,024
I'll be in New York with Walter!

713
00:46:25,199 --> 00:46:27,159
Do you wanna hear about destiny?

714
00:46:27,326 --> 00:46:28,702
If I hadn't married Martin

715
00:46:28,870 --> 00:46:30,954
I never would've bought
the house with
the dead tree.

716
00:46:31,122 --> 00:46:33,081
On account of which I got divorced.

717
00:46:33,249 --> 00:46:37,335
On account of which
I hit a car and met Rick
