718
00:46:37,503 --> 00:46:41,756
Wait a minute. You never
told me you got a divorce
because of a dead tree?

719
00:46:42,675 --> 00:46:46,052
The tree man.
You fell in love with the tree man?

720
00:46:46,220 --> 00:46:49,139
