Did I say "love"?

721
00:46:49,557 --> 00:46:52,100
This is my favourite part.

722
00:46:53,519 --> 00:46:55,770
It's now or never.

723
00:46:56,481 --> 00:46:58,940
Never is a frightening word.

724
00:46:59,942 --> 00:47:02,611
We'd be fools to let happiness pass us by.

725
00:47:02,778 --> 00:47:04,196
KERR:
Uh-huh.

726
00:47:05,907 --> 00:47:10,202
Winter must be cold
for those with
no warm memories.

727
00:47:12,288 --> 00:47:16,082
We've already missed the spring.
GRANT: Yes.

728
00:47:17,460 --> 00:47:19,461
Men never get this movie.

729
00:47:19,629 --> 00:47:21,421
I know.

