752
00:48:40,084 --> 00:48:42,961
About you.
How you're doing.

753
00:48:43,588 --> 00:48:47,465
Which she sort of knows, but I tell her anyway.

754
00:48:47,675 --> 00:48:49,676
So, what is that?

755
00:48:51,804 --> 00:48:54,139
It's sort of an afterlife, isn't it?

756
00:48:55,099 --> 00:48:56,891
I'm starting to forget her.

757
00:49:13,159 --> 00:49:16,828
She could peel an apple

758
