00:51:06,021 --> 00:51:07,397
Laurie?

784
00:51:07,565 --> 00:51:09,190
Hi, it's Annie.

785
00:51:09,358 --> 00:51:11,317
Fine, fine. I'm fine.

786
00:51:11,485 --> 00:51:14,988
Listen, I'm doing an article
on call-in radio shows.

787
00:51:15,156 --> 00:51:18,992
Do you know anyone who works
for someone named
Dr. Marcia Fieldstone?

788
00:51:19,201 --> 00:51:22,328
I'm a writer for the Baltimore Sun,
