789
00:51:22,496 --> 00:51:25,039
I'm doing a piece on how people
handle bereavement.

790
00:51:25,207 --> 00:51:29,169
And I understand you had
a caller the other night,
some guy from Seattle.

791
00:51:37,344 --> 00:51:40,764
JONAH [ON MACHINE]:
This is Jonah Baldwin.
We're not in right now, but you can...

792
00:51:41,474 --> 00:51:42,557
Baldwin.

793
00:51:42,808 --> 00:51:44,893
[♪♪♪]

794
00:52:45,162 --> 00:52:46,538
Architect.

795
00:53:20,114 --> 00:53:21,990
Psst.
SAM: Okay, Clarise.

796
00:53:22,157 --> 00:53:26,870
I'm gonna be back either by
midnight or 8:30,
if disaster strikes.

797
00:53:27,037 --> 00:53:31,875
Here's one for the both of us.
"Sleepless and Son, Baltimore."

798
00:53:32,042 --> 00:53:35,420
If there's any problem,
