00:54:21,467 --> 00:54:24,177
Everyone thinks so.
It's a sign.

815
00:54:24,845 --> 00:54:26,471
Come here.

816
00:54:26,805 --> 00:54:29,015
I'll show you a sign.
Here's a sign.

817
00:54:29,516 --> 00:54:31,184
All right.

818
00:54:31,644 --> 00:54:33,061
Where's Seattle?

819
00:54:33,228 --> 00:54:35,521
Right. Where is Baltimore?

820
00:54:35,940 --> 00:54:38,232
Ah! It's right there! Look!

821
00:54:38,400 --> 00:54:43,029
One, two, three.
There's, like, 26 states between
here and there. Now, that's a sign.

822
00:54:43,197 --> 00:54:47,909
I'm out of here. Goodbye!
Good night! I love you.

823
00:54:51,413 --> 00:54:53,289
Clarise, did you move your car?

824
00:54:53,457 --> 00:54:54,457
Huh?

825
00:54:54,625 --> 00:54:55,875
[SAM GRUMBLES]

826
00:55:03,592 --> 00:55:06,219
Thank you, Derrick.
You're welcome.

827
00:55:06,387 --> 00:55:07,887
I'll have...
White wine spritzer?

828
00:55:08,097 --> 00:55:09,430
Yes.
And you, sir?

829
00:55:09,598 --> 00:55:10,974
I'm fine. Thank you.

830
00:55:11,141 --> 00:55:12,183
Hi.
Hi.

831
00:55:12,351 --> 00:55:16,187
You look good.
You look good yourself.

832
00:55:20,651 --> 00:55:23,027
I thought you'd never call me.

833
00:55:23,195 --> 00:55:24,737
You did?
I really wanted you to.

834
00:55:24,947 --> 00:55:26,864
And I thought you were never going to.

835
00:55:27,032 --> 00:55:28,658
MAN: Excuse me, Mr. Baldwin?
Yes.

836
00:55:28,826 --> 00:55:31,119
There's a phone call for you.

837
00:55:31,996 --> 00:55:33,538
Excuse me.

838
00:55:38,168 --> 00:55:39,711
Thank you. Hello.

839
00:55:39,920 --> 00:55:43,006
JONAH: Dad, can we go to
New York City
