of the Empire State Building
on Valentine's Day.

842
00:55:51,932 --> 00:55:53,850
Jonah?
What?

843
00:55:54,018 --> 00:55:56,436
Have you fallen down?
Are you bleeding?

844
00:55:56,603 --> 00:55:58,688
Is Clarise there?
Has she been strangled?

845
00:55:58,856 --> 00:56:01,441
No.
This is the only reason for this call?

846
00:56:01,608 --> 00:56:04,318
If we book now, we can get an excursion fare.

847
00:56:04,486 --> 00:56:09,323
Jessica's parents are travel agents...
I'm not having this conversation.

848
00:56:09,533 --> 00:56:11,492
We'll talk about it at a later time.

849
00:56:11,660 --> 00:56:15,038
I can't believe
this conversation has lasted
this long. You go to bed.

850
00:56:22,713 --> 00:56:24,881
Everything all right?
Oh, yeah.

851
00:56:25,299 --> 00:56:26,883
Do you have kids?
No.

852
00:56:27,051 --> 00:56:28,509
Do you want mine?

853
00:56:28,677 --> 00:56:30,470
[LAUGHS]

854
00:56:31,305 --> 00:56:33,639
