863
00:57:06,507 --> 00:57:08,341
You must be Jonah.

864
00:57:10,427 --> 00:57:12,011
Hi.

865
00:57:12,429 --> 00:57:13,763
So this it?
Yeah.

866
00:57:13,972 --> 00:57:16,516
The car's down this way.
Great.

867
00:57:17,309 --> 00:57:21,229
She's on her sixth painter
and we are never going
to finish this job.

868
00:57:21,396 --> 00:57:24,232
Now she wants the fireplace rebricked.

869
00:57:24,399 --> 00:57:26,359
I know her.
I could give her a call.

870
00:57:26,527 --> 00:57:29,987
No, I've got it solved.
I'll just hit her with
one of those bricks.

871
00:57:30,155 --> 00:57:33,282
[VICTORIA LAUGHING]

872
00:57:33,450 --> 00:57:36,494
That's so funny.
You're so funny.

873
00:57:36,662 --> 00:57:42,708
When she wants something
done she says, "Oh, I don't know.
I'm stupid. You know what's best.

874
00:57:42,876 --> 00:57:48,131
But couldn't we flip the house
around so that everything in
the back is now in front?

875
00:57:48,298 --> 00:57:54,387
And could the whole front
of the house open on a hinge
