903
01:00:21,785 --> 01:00:24,787
I'll go downstairs.
Becky, I'll call you back.

904
01:00:27,624 --> 01:00:30,293
I'm sorry, Walter.
Are you bleeding?

905
01:00:30,460 --> 01:00:32,503
[WALTER GRUNTS AND GROANS]

