01:00:37,134 --> 01:00:39,343
[WHEEZES]

907
01:00:43,974 --> 01:00:46,309
[♪♪♪]

908
01:00:51,315 --> 01:00:53,274
JONAH:
He's kissing her right this minute!

909
01:00:53,442 --> 01:00:54,483
FIELDSTONE:
Oh, really?

910
01:00:54,651 --> 01:00:58,446
Jonah, tell the truth:
